{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "techx-todo-api-collection",
    "name": "TechX Todo API",
    "description": "Collection para testar a API do desafio TechX To-Do List.\n\n## Setup\n1. Importe esta collection e o environment `local.postman_environment.json`\n2. Selecione o environment **TechX Todo - Local**\n3. Suba os bancos: `docker compose up -d`\n4. Rode a API: `cd backend && npm run dev`\n5. Execute **Auth > Register** ou **Auth > Login** — o token é salvo automaticamente\n\n## Endpoints implementados\n- Health\n- Auth (register, login)\n\n## Endpoints planejados (Fase 4+)\nA pasta **Tasks** contém requests que exigem autenticação e serão habilitados na Fase 4.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "taskId",
      "value": "1"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica status da API, MySQL e MongoDB."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Returns token', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Matheus Soares\",\n  \"email\": \"matheus@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Cadastra um novo usuário. Retorna JWT e dados do usuário (sem senha)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns token', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"matheus@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica usuário existente. Retorna JWT."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register - Validation Error (example)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"A\",\n  \"email\": \"invalid-email\",\n  \"password\": \"123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Exemplo de payload inválido — esperado 400 com details de validação."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tasks (Fase 4)",
      "description": "Endpoints protegidos por JWT. Disponíveis após implementação da Fase 4.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Tasks",
